This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it presents a method for synapse detection using semantic segmentation. It may also belong to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category as it deals with the wiring diagram of the brain. Additionally, it could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves developing a fully automated system. Finally, it may also belong to the software engineering (cs.SD) sub-category as it discusses improvements in scalability.
